Lyrics-Fetcher-LeosLyrics README
====================================

Lyrics::Fetcher::LeosLyrics, as the name suggests, fetches lyrics
from www.leoslyrics.com using it's unpublished XML interface. 

It is intended to be used as a fetcher by Lyrics::Fetcher, but
can be used on its own if you desire.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 XML::Simple;
 LWP::Simple;
 URI::Escape


Calling Lyrics::Fetcher::LeosLyrics via Lyrics::Fetcher->fetch() is
recommended, but you can call Lyrics::Fetcher::LeosLyrics->fetch() directly
if you want to do so.

